(23, 9, '2016-10-21 19:58:09', '2016-10-21 19:58:09', '<div class = "getInvolvedImage">\r\n<img class="fullWidth" src="/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/getinvolved_hero.jpg" />\r\n<span class = "helpTop">\r\n<h4>HOW YOU CAN HELP</h4>\r\n<p>On the surface, child sex-trafficking can seem like too big of a problem to tackle. However, the strength of our organization is together our voices can and will make a difference.</p>\r\n</span>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="getInvolvedContainer">\r\n<h2>DONATE</h2>\r\n<h4 class="donateDesc">With each donation, Amplified Voices will fund ways to consolidate the forces working against child sex trafficking:</h4>\r\n<p class="donateDesc">-turning up the volume so that victim and survivor voices are heard</p>\r\n<p class="donateDesc">-supporting long-term plans for prevention, outreach and survivor services</p>\r\n<button class="giveButton" type="button"><i class="fa fa-long-arrow-right" aria-hidden="true"></i> GIVE NOW</button>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="volunteerContainer">\r\n<div class="row">\r\n<div class="col-md-6"><img src="/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/getInvolved.png" alt="getinvolved" width="500" height="500" /></div>\r\n<div class="col-md-6">\r\n<h4>VOLUNTEER</h4>\r\nThe more voices, the more clearly we are heard. Interested in joining us? Every helping hand is welcome.\r\n<h4>HOST A FUNDRAISER</h4>\r\nOur amplification efforts depend on grassroots funding to augment foundation giving. If you are interested in hosting an Amplified Voices fundraiser, then you can make a significant impact on ending child sex-trafficking.\r\n<button class="emailEvents" type="button"><i class="fa fa-long-arrow-right" aria-hidden="true"></i> EMAIL OUR EVENTS COORDINATOR</button>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="involvedEventsContainer">\r\n<h2>EVENTS</h2>\r\n<h4>Across the nation, there are events that specifically focus on and raise awareness of child sex-trafficking. Find one near you.</h4>\r\n<button class="involvedButton" type="button"><i class="fa fa-long-arrow-right" aria-hidden="true"></i> SEE OUR CALENDAR</button>\r\n<h2>ARTICLES</h2>\r\n<h4>We\'re always keeping an eye on the latest in the fight against child sex-trafficking. Check back often to see what we\'ve added.</h4>\r\n<button class="involvedButton" type="button"><i class="fa fa-long-arrow-right" aria-hidden="true"></i> SEE RECENT ARTICLES</button>\r\n\r\n</div>', 'Get Involved', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'get-involved', '', '', '2016-11-08 22:49:40', '2016-11-08 22:49:40', '', 0, 'http://www.thedirtysix.dev/?page_id=10', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(25, 1, '2016-10-21 19:58:22', '2016-10-21 19:58:22', '<div class = "donateImage">\r\n<img class="fullwidth" src="/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/donate_hero.jpg" />\r\n<span class = "donateTop">\r\n<h2>YOUR GIFT IS THE BEGINNING OF A MOVEMENT.</h2>\r\n<button type = "button" class = "donateOnlineButton"><i class="fa fa-long-arrow-right" aria-hidden="true"></i> DONATE ONLINE</button>\r\n</span>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class ="donateContainer">\r\n<h4>Imagine the end of child sex-trafficking, a time when our country has reached a level of awareness, commitment and action that makes the sex trafficking industry impossible to sustain.</h4>\r\n<h2>IT\'S A VISION WE BELIEVE IN AND A PLACE WE CAN GET TO WITH YOUR HELP</h2>\r\n<h4>Your dollars will support efforts such as turning up the volume so that victim and survivor voices are heard and bring together advocates, law enforcement and more to identify solutions tailored to the needs of local communities.</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class = "sponsorsContainer">\r\n<h2>We thank our founding and corporate sponsors.</h2>\r\n<h5 class = "sponsors">--FOUNDING SPONSORS</h5>\r\n<h5>Sample Sponsor</h5>\r\n<h5 class = "donors">--DONORS</h5>\r\n<h5>Sample Donor</h5>\r\n<h5 class = "supporters">--SUPPORTERS</h5>\r\n<h5>Sample Supporter</h5>\r\n</div>', 'Donate', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'donate', '', '', '2016-11-08 23:28:37', '2016-11-08 23:28:37', '', 0, 'http://www.thedirtysix.dev/?page_id=12', 0, 'page', '', 0),
