(98, 1, '2016-10-28 18:11:29', '2016-10-28 18:11:29', '<img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-57" src="http://localhost/thedirtysix.php56-11.dfw3-2.websitetestlink.com/wp-content/uploads/1_home_hero.jpg" alt="1_home_hero" width="11667" height="6946" />\r\n<h1></h1>\r\n<h1>CHILD SEX TRAFFICKING MUST STOP</h1>\r\n<h4>Every month, 213 children are sold for sex five times per day <span style="margin: 0px; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Calibri\',sans-serif; font-size: 11pt;"><span style="color: #000000;">— </span></span> in Minnesota alone.</h4>\r\nADD YOUR VOICE [button]\r\n<h2><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-93" src="/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/amplify.png" alt="amplify" width="55" height="50" /></h2>\r\n<h2>AMPLIFY</h2>\r\nLandmark sporting events attract hundreds of millions of media impressions, which provides a massive megaphone that we\'ll leverage to spread our message.\r\n<h2><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-93" src="/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/amplify.png" alt="amplify" width="55" height="50" /></h2>\r\n<h2>ASSEMBLE</h2>\r\nWe will convene a table of stakeholders and the voices of the victims from city to city and create a web of awareness and support across the country.\r\n<h2><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-94" src="/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/assemble.png" alt="assemble" width="76" height="50" /></h2>\r\n<h2>ACTION</h2>\r\nAction starts with awareness, but we won\'t stop there. We will provide a lasting legacy of support devoted to the fight against child sex trafficking.\r\n\r\nSEE OUR PLAN [button]\r\n\r\n<img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-49" src="http://localhost/thedirtysix.php56-11.dfw3-2.websitetestlink.com/wp-content/uploads/2_home_hero.jpg" alt="&quot;&quot;" width="11273" height="8730" />\r\n<h1>LET\'S BE HEARD</h1>\r\nGET INVOLVED [button]\r\n<h1>OUR SINCEREST THANKS TO OUR EARLY SUPPORTERS</h1>\r\n<h4>We could not have started this movement without your generosity.</h4>\r\nKnock [logo]\r\n\r\nRonins Kaplan [logo]\r\n\r\nShapco Printing {logo]\r\n\r\nSEE ALL SPONSORS [button]\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'Home', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '12-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-10-28 18:11:29', '2016-10-28 18:11:29', '', 12, '/98', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
