(99, 3, '2016-10-28 18:13:53', '2016-10-28 18:13:53', '<!-- Section 1 -->\r\n<!-- background image: ../5_getinvolved_hero-300x139.jpg; text color: #ff5a59 -->\r\n<img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-85" src="/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/5_getinvolved_hero-300x139.jpg" alt="5_getinvolved_hero" width="300" height="139" />\r\n<h4>HOW YOU CAN HELP</h4>\r\nChild sex trafficking can seem like too big a problem to tackle. The strength of our organization is that together, our voices can and will make a difference.\r\n<!-- End Section 1 -->\r\n<!-- Section 2 -->\r\n<!-- background color: #ff5a58; text color: white -->\r\n<h1>DONATE</h1>\r\nWith each donation, Amplified Voices will fund ways to consolidate the forces working against child sex trafficking:\r\n<!-- bulleted list -->\r\nturning up the volume so that victim and survivor voices are heard\r\nsupporting long term plans for prevention, outreach, and survivor services\r\n\r\n<!-- button: background: white; text: #ff5a59 -->\r\nGIVE NOW\r\n<!-- End Section 2 -->\r\n\r\n<!-- Section 3 -->\r\n<!-- background: white -->\r\n<!-- 3.1 - left -->\r\n<!-- image: ../6_getinvolved_inline-300x200.jpg -->\r\n<!-- Reduce width to make square, needs thin white border and ?drop shadow? in #ff5a59 -->\r\n<img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-7" src="http://www.thedirtysix.dev/wp/content/uploads/2016/10/6_getinvolved_inline-300x200.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="200" />\r\n\r\n<!-- 3.1 - right -->\r\n<!-- text: #ff5a59 -->\r\n<h4>VOLUNTEER</h4>\r\nThe more voices, the more clearly we are heard. Interested in joining us? Every helping hand is welcome.\r\n<h4>HOST A FUNDRAISER</h4>\r\nOur amplification efforts depends on grassroots funding to augment foundation giving. If you are interested in hosting an Amplified Voices fundraiser, you can make a significant impact on ending child sex trafficking.\r\n\r\n<!-- button: background: #ff5a59; text: white -->\r\nEMAIL OUR EVENTS COORDINATOR\r\n\r\n<!-- 3.2 -->\r\n<!-- text: #a0359