(134, 1, '2016-11-02 18:49:51', '2016-11-02 18:49:51', '<!-- Section 1 -->\n<!-- background image: ../5_getinvolved_hero-300x139.jpg; text color: #ff5a59 -->\n<img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-85" src="/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/5_getinvolved_hero.jpg" alt="5_getinvolved_hero" width="9689" height="4500" />\n<h4>HOW YOU CAN HELP</h4>\nOn the surface, child sex-trafficking can seem like too big of a problem to tackle. However, the strength of our organization is together our voices can and will make a difference.\n<!-- End Section 1 -->\n<!-- Section 2 -->\n<!-- background color: #ff5a58; text color: white -->\n<h1>DONATE</h1>\nWith each donation, Amplified Voices will fund ways to consolidate the forces working against child sex trafficking:turning up the volume so that victim and survivor voices are heard\n\nturning up the volume so that victim and survivor voices are heard\nsupporting long-term plans for prevention, outreach and survivor services\n\n<!-- button: background: white; text: #ff5a59 -->\nGIVE NOW\n<!-- Reduce width to make square, needs thin white border and ?drop shadow? in #ff5a59 -->\n<img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-100" src="/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/6_getinvolved_inline.jpg" alt="6_getinvolved_inline" width="4500" height="2996" />\n\n<!-- 3.1 - right -->\n<!-- text: #ff5a59 -->\n<h4>VOLUNTEER</h4>\nThe more voices, the more clearly we are heard. Interested in joining us? Every helping hand is welcome.\n<h4>HOST A FUNDRAISER</h4>\nOur amplification efforts depend on grassroots funding to augment foundation giving. If you are interested in hosting an Amplified Voices fundraiser, then you can make a significant impact on ending child sex-trafficking.\n\nEMAIL OUR EVENTS COORDINATOR\n\n<strong>EVENTS</strong>\n\nAcross the nation, there are events that specifically focus on and raise awareness of child sex trafficking. Find one near you.\n\nSEE OUR CALENDAR\n\n<strong>ARTICLES</strong>\n\nWe\'re always keeping an eye on the latest in the fight against child sex-trafficking. Check back often to see what we\'ve added.\n\n<!-- button: background: #a03594; text: white -->\nSEE RECENT ARTICLES', 'Get Involved', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '23-autosave-v1', '', '', '2016-11-02 18:49:51', '2016-11-02 18:49:51', '', 23, '/134', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
