ld working as a senior marketing and product design executive for companies such as Marshall Field’s, Manhattan Toy and Blip Toys. She\'s crafted compelling marketing messages and has overseen the creation and production of child-centered products.<br>She has witnessed global human trafficking\'s core — poverty — first-hand during her travels in China, Hong Kong, Indonesia and throughout Southeast Asia.Closer to home, Clea attended grade school in Grand Portage Reservation, Minnesota, and saw how crushing poverty hasn\'t been exclusive to foreign countries. A passion for human rights and women’s issues drove her to continuously strive to help and give back to the communities in which she grew up.<br>Clea lives in Minneapolis, Minnesota, with her husband, Thomas Zeis, and their 13-year-old son Davis and 10-year-old daughter Aurora.</p>\r\n\r\n<div class = "container" id = "aboutBackground">\r\n<img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-120" src="/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/megaphone.png" alt="megaphone" width="250" height="250" />\r\n<div class = "row">\r\n<div class = "col-md-4">\r\n<h1 class ="aboutTitle">Amplify</h1>\r\n<h4 class = "aboutDesc">Landmark sporting events attract hundreds of millions of media impressions, which provide a massive megaphone that we’ll leverage to spread our message.</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class = "col-md-4">\r\n<p class = "example">For example, there will be an estimated 112 million viewers of the 2018 Super Bowl, with 5,000 media professionals covering the event.<br>We will spread the message via a robust media campaign, a recognizable social call-to-action, messaging partnerships with hospitality and the travel industry.<br>Amplified support from notable national figures and cause-minded celebrities.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h1><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-121" src="/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/people.png" alt="people" width="250" height="250" /></h1>\r\n<div class = "row">\r\n<div class = "col-md-4">\r\n<h1 class ="aboutTitle">Assemble</h1>\r\n<h4 class = "aboutDesc">We will convene a table of stakeholders and the voices of the victims from city to city, which will create a web of awareness and support across the country.</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class = "col-md-4">\r\n<p class = "example">Not creating a silo will bring together non-profits, policy makers, law enforcement and nationally recognized experts.<br>Learnings are documented and travel to inform efforts in each new host city.<br>Solutions tailored to the needs of the local host committees will be sought by action-oriented moderators.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h1><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-119" src="/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/fist.png" alt="fist" width="250" height="250" /></h1>\r\n<div class = "row">\r\n<div class = "col-md-4">\r\n<h1 class ="aboutTitle">Action</h1>\r\n<h4 class = "aboutDesc">Action starts with awareness, but we won’t stop there. We will provide a lasting legacy of support devoted to the fight against child sex-trafficking.</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class = "col-md-4">\r\n<p class = "example">We will develop a fund that will provide emergency resources via conditional grants to victims.<br>Grants to local stakeholders to further their work in the fight to stop sex trafficking.<br>Create connections between like-minded efforts, nationally.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h4 class = "quoteBottom">Because together</h4>\r\n<h1 class = "quoteBottom">Our Voices Cannot Be Ignored</h1>', 'About', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '16-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-11-05 05:46:21', '2016-11-05 05:46:21', '', 16, '/180', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
