(208, 5, '2016-11-07 05:10:18', '2016-11-07 05:10:18', '<div class = "getInvolvedImage">\n<img class="fullWidth" src="/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/5_getinvolved_hero.jpg" alt="5_getinvolved_hero" width="9689" height="4500" />\n<span class = "helpTop">\n<h4>HOW YOU CAN HELP</h4>\n<p>On the surface, child sex-trafficking can seem like too big of a problem to tackle. However, the strength of our organization is together our voices can and will make a difference.</p>\n</span>\n</div>\n\n<div class="getInvolvedContainer">\n<h2>DONATE</h2>\n<h4 class="donateDesc">With each donation, Amplified Voices will fund ways to consolidate the forces working against child sex trafficking:</h4>\n<p class="donateDesc">-turning up the volume so that victim and survivor voices are heard</p>\n<p class="donateDesc">-supporting long-term plans for prevention, outreach and survivor services</p>\n<button class="giveButton" type="button"><i class="fa fa-long-arrow-right" aria-hidden="true"></i> GIVE NOW</button>\n\n</div>\n<div class="volunteerContainer">\n<div class="row">\n<div class="col-md-6"><img src="/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/getInvolved.png" alt="getinvolved" width="500" height="500" /></div>\n<div class="col-md-6">\n<h4>VOLUNTEER</h4>\nThe more voices, the more clearly we are heard. Interested in joining us? Every helping hand is welcome.\n<h4>HOST A FUNDRAISER</h4>\nOur amplification efforts depend on grassroots funding to augment foundation giving. If you are interested in hosting an Amplified Voices fundraiser, then you can make a significant impact on ending child sex-trafficking.\n<button class="emailEvents" type="button"><i class="fa fa-long-arrow-right" aria-hidden="true"></i> EMAIL OUR EVENTS COORDINATOR</button>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="involvedEventsContainer">\n<h2>EVENTS</h2>\n<h4>Across the nation, there are events that specifically focus on and raise awareness of child sex-trafficking. Find one near you.</h4>\n<button class="involvedButton" type="button">SEE OUR CALENDAR</button>\n<h2>ARTICLES</h2>\n<h4>We\'re always keeping an eye on the latest in the fight against child sex-trafficking. Check back often to see what we\'ve added.</h4>\n<button class="involvedButton" type="button"><i class="fa fa-long-arrow-right" aria-hidden="true"></i> SEE RECENT ARTICLES</button>\n\n</div>', 'Get Involved', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '23-autosave-v1', '', '', '2016-11-07 05:10:18', '2016-11-07 05:10:18', '', 23, '/208', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
