(229, 5, '2016-11-07 03:57:56', '2016-11-07 03:57:56', '<div class = "homeImage">\n<img class="aligncenter wp-image-83 size-full" src="/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/1_home_hero-e1478109662420.jpg" alt="&quot;&quot;" width="1720" height="1024" />\n<span class ="homeTop">\n<h4>Every month, 213 children are sold for sex 5 times a day.</h4><br>\n<h4>In Minnesota alone.</h4>\n<h2>CHILD SEX TRAFFICKING MUST STOP</h2>\n<button input = "button" class = "voiceButton">ADD YOUR VOICE</button>\n</span>\n</div>\n<div class = "homeContainer">\n<div class = "row">\n<div class = "col-md-4">\n<h2><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-93" src="/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/amplify.png" alt="amplify" width="55" height="50" /></h2>\n</div>\n<div class = "col-md-4">\n<h2><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-93" src="/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/amplify.png" alt="amplify" width="55" height="50" /></h2>\n</div>\n<div class = "col-md-4">\n<h2><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-94" src="/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/assemble.png" alt="assemble" width="76" height="50" /></h2>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class = "row">\n<div class = "col-md-4">\n<h3>AMPLIFY</h3>\n<h5>We will leverage landmark sporting events, such as professional football\'s big game, to attract hundreds of millions of media impressions.</h5>\n<button input = "button" class ="planButton">SEE OUR PLAN</button>\n</div>\n<div class = "col-md-4">\n<h3>ASSEMBLE</h3>\n<h5>We will convene a table of stakeholders and the voices of the victims from city to city to create a web of awareness and support across the country.</h5>\n</div>\n<div class = "col-md-4">\n<h3>ACTION</h3>\n<h5>Action starts with awareness, but we won\'t stop there. We will provide a lasting legacy of support devoted to the fight against child sex trafficking.</h5>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class = "heardImage">\n<img class="fullwidth" src="/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/2_home_hero-e1478109459136.jpg" alt="&quot;&quot;" width="1322" height="1024" />\n<span class 