(327, 1, '2016-11-08 18:18:07', '2016-11-08 18:18:07', '<div class="sponsorsCopy">\r\n<h1>SPONSORS</h1>\r\n<h4>Thank you to all of our sponsors. Together we can end child sex-trafficking.</h4>\r\n<h6><a href="mailto:info@amplifiedvoicesnow.org">Email us</a> to become a sponsor.</h6>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="sponsorsLogos"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-300" src="/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/Shapco-logo.png" alt="Shapco Printing" width="125" height="34" /><img class="alignnone size-thumbnail wp-image-299" src="/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/Robins-kaplan-logo-150x14.png" alt="Robins Kaplan" width="150" height="14" /><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-298" src="/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/Knock-logo.png" alt="Knock Inc." width="107" height="22" /><img class="alignnone size-thumbnail wp-image-296" src="/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/mdewakanton-logo-150x150.jpg" alt="mdewakanton" width="150" height="150" /></div>', 'Sponsors', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '305-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-11-08 18:18:07', '2016-11-08 18:18:07', '', 305, '/305-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(328, 5, '2016-11-08 22:18:19', '2016-11-08 22:18:19', '<div class = "aboutImage">\r\n<img class = "aligncenter wp-image-83 size-full" src = "/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/3_about_hero.jpg"width="1720" height="1024">\r\n<span class = "top">\r\n<h2>Vision</h2>\r\n<p>A world without child sex trafficking.</p>\r\n</span>\r\n<span class = "bottom">\r\n<h2>Mission</h2>\r\n<p>To fight child sex-trafficking and create a lasting legacy of public awareness and resources through the megaphone of major media events.</hp>\r\n</span>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class = "aboutContainer">\r\n<div class = "quote">\r\n<h4>For us it\'s about doing something now.</h4>\r\n<h2>NOW IS THE TIME TO CREATE A MOVEMENT THAT ENDS CHILD SEX-TRAFFICKING FOR GOOD.</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class = "row">\r\n<div class = "col-md-6">\r\n<h4 class = "bioName">Sarah Perron</h4><h5 class = "bioTitle">, Amplified Voices founder</h5><br>\r\n<p class = "bioDescription">Sarah has been at the forefront of the advertising and digital marketing world for two decades. She has experience at global agencies that includes groundbreaking work for Starwood Hotels, Target, Ameriprise, Best Buy and BMW Films, where she helped steer “The Driver” into a worldwide viral video phenomenon.<br>Her career began in the early days of Geek Squad, where she established marketing and PR efforts that supported the company’s distinctive brand. More recently, she\'s worked for KNOCK Inc. — a design and strategy firm in Minneapolis, Minnesota — as director of digital integration.<br>Throughout her career, Sarah has worked tirelessly advocating for women and children with a focus on homelessness, abuse and sexual exploitation. For example, she served as a board member of WATCH and also served for many years as a volunteer at Free Arts MN. Currently, Sarah serves as a board member of The Link and as vice chair of Harriet Tubman Center Board of Directors.Sarah lives in Minneapolis with her husband, Tom, and seven-year-old daughter, Lilly.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class = "col-md-6">\r\n<h4 class = "bioName">Clea Korf</h4><h5 class = "bioTitle">, Amplified Voices founder</h5><br>\r\n<p class = "bioDescription">Clea has traveled the world working as a senior marketing and product design executive for companies such as Marshall Field’s, Manhattan Toy and Blip Toys. She\'s crafted compelling marketing messages and has overseen the creation and production of child-centered products.<br>She has witnessed global human trafficking\'s core — poverty — first-hand during her travels in China, Hong Kong, Indonesia and throughout Southeast Asia.Closer to home, Clea attended grade school in Grand Portage Reservation, Minnesota, and saw how crushing poverty hasn\'t been exclusive to foreign countries. A passion for human rights and women’s issues drove her to continuously strive to help and give back to the communities in which she grew up.<br>Clea lives in Minneapolis, Minnesota, with her husband, Thomas Zeis, and their 13-year-old son Davis and 10-year-old daughter Aurora.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class = "fullwidth" id = "aboutBackground">\r\n<div class = "aboutContainer">\r\n<img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-120" src="/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/megaphone.png" alt="megaphone" width="250" height="250" />\r\n<div class = "row">\r\n<div class = "col-md-6">\r\n<h1 class ="aboutTitle">Amplify</h1>\r\n<h4 class = "aboutDesc">Landmark sporting events attract hundreds of millions of media impressions, which provide a massive megaphone that we’ll leverage to spread our message.</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class = "col-md-6">\r\n<p class = "example">For example, there will be an estimated 112 million viewers of the 2018 Super Bowl, with 5,000 media professionals covering the event.<br>We will spread the message via a robust media campaign, a recognizable social call-to-action, messaging partnerships with hospitality and the travel industry.<br>Amplified support from notable national figures and cause-minded celebrities.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h1><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-121" src="/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/people.png" alt="people" width="250" height="250" /></h1>\r\n<div class = "row">\r\n<div class = "col-md-6">\r\n<h1 class ="aboutTitle">Assemble</h1>\r\n<h4 class = "aboutDesc">We will convene a table of stakeholders and the voices of the victims from city to city, which will create a web of awareness and support across the country.</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class = "col-md-6">\r\n<p class = "example">Not creating a silo will bring together non-profits, policy makers, law enforcement and nationally recognized experts.<br>Learnings are documented and travel to inform efforts in each new host city.<br>Solutions tailored to the needs of the local host committees will be sought by action-oriented moderators.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h1><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-119" src="/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/fist.png" alt="fist" width="250" height="250" /></h1>\r\n<div class = "row">\r\n<div class = "col-md-6">\r\n<h1 class ="aboutTitle">Action</h1>\r\n<h4 class = "aboutDesc">Action starts with awareness, but we won’t stop there. We will provide a lasting legacy of support devoted to the fight against child sex-trafficking.</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class = "col-md-6">\r\n<p class = "example">We will develop a fund that will provide emergency resources via conditional grants to victims.<br>Grants to local stakeholders to further their work in the fight to stop sex trafficking.<br>Create connections between like-minded efforts, nationally.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class = "aboutContainer">\r\n<h4 class = "quoteBottom">Because together,</h4>\r\n<h2 class = "quoteBottom">Our Voices Cannot Be Ignored.</h2>\r\n</div>', 'About', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '16-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-11-08 22:18:19', '2016-11-08 22:18:19', '', 16, '/16-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
